name: Italian Chain Bracelet
description:
Italian jewelry is know for its dainty unique design, culture, fine craftsmanship and much more. This Italian multi-chain bracelet with spiral tube detailing is perfect to wear by it's self or stacked with other bracelets to add on to your day outfit and even dressing up your evening wear.

Details: 
14k gold filled 
Twisted curb chain detail
Spiral tube
Adjustable links at closure 
Fits standard size wrist (7 - 7 1/2")
Available in: Yellow, White, Rose & Oxidized (black) Gold

name: Trio Gold Italian Bracelet
description:
Lovely Italian chain bracelet with disco ball bead detail. The mixed gold tones of white, rose and oxidized is a look that is simple enough but yet still making a statement to your daily outfit.

Details:
14k gold filled 
Rope curb chain
Faceted bead detail
Adjustable links at closure 
Fits standard size wrist (7 - 7 1/2")
